latestPosts.caption:
RCB fans, where ya’all at?

IPL is fixed, they say. As an RCB fan of at least a decade, I couldn’t care less. I said everytime, ‘i’ll stop watching IPL if RCB doesn’t win this season’, and yet, came back every single time! Everything for just one person — Virat Kohli! 

The boys played well. PBKS did well too, but it was just not the day!

EE SALA CUP NAMDU! 💃🏼✨

Instagram is already painted red, for the love of RCB, Virat Kohli and everyone who’s been a part of this journey!

Maybe, 2025 is going to be different after all ♥️

latestPosts.caption: Decided to wear a suit just because ✨✨

Some more propagandas I am definitely falling for include -

💌 Being pretty does not mean being thin.

💌 Some people think of themselves too highly, let them, as long as it doesn’t affect you.

💌 Being vocal will help you get rid of people.

💌 No one gets to decide how you deal with grief, emotions, and your weak moments.

💌 Life’s not stopping, with or without anyone.

💌 Some people will never truly be happy for your success, so don’t forget the 🧿🧿🧿🧿🧿🧿🧿🧿🧿🧿🧿🧿🧿🧿🧿🧿🧿🧿🧿

💌 Only love is never enough.

💌 You can only do much for people, because chances are, they’ll be thankless either way.
